dct_title_s: Clavdii Et Traiani Impp Admirabilivm Portvvm Ostiensivm Orthographia
dct_alternative_sm: Claudii et Traiani impp admirabilium portuum ostiensium orthographia
dct_description_sm: Per Stephanvm Dv Perach Architectvm Ivxta Antiqva Vestigia Accvratissime Delineata. Ambrosius brambila f.

Classical city view, title cartouche at lower left with Van Schoel's name beneath, ancient buildings, harbor and large harbor statue, ancient ships, walls, acqueduct, hinterland, elaborate waves, watermark.
